MultiChoice is extending access to its DStv Now service to all DStv Premium customers. “Previously, the full DStv Now service was only available to DStv Premium customers with an active PVR,” said MultiChoice. “Premium customers can now enjoy more than 60 live DStv channels.” Customers can use their smartphone or tablet to watch or download series and movies, with the content library including the M-Net Movie Collection. This offers 1,000 movies that are updated weekly. Live streaming from SuperSport channels is also supported. “DStv Now can also be used to access Express from the US shows on M-Net – which are available within hours of their US broadcast.” Other features of DStv Now include: The DStv Now app is available for iOS and Android. It is also available online at DStv.com.